1133 Regent Street is a four (4) storey plus penthouse office building constructed circa 1983 with a 22,000 sq. ft. floor plate. The85,614 sq. ft. building is 100% leased with a weighted average lease expiry of 3.5 years. Key tenants include Government of Canada including Passport Services, and Department of National Defense, New Brunswick Association of Nursing Homes, PinkLarkin Law, Investors Group Financial and EXP Services. The tenant mix and expiry profile results in 1133 Regent being an excellent investment opportunity in New Brunswicks capital.
